# Fudi Docs Rule

- Keep documentation current with architecture and product decisions.
- Prefer concise, structured Markdown with tables and checklists.
- Document role boundaries, environment separation, integrations and deployment implications.
- If a product decision reduces scope, explain why.
- Keep agent prompts focused, deterministic and scoped to their specialization.
